{"title_page": "Srikail Gas Field", "text_new": "{{Infobox Oil field\n| name = Srikail Gas Field\n| region = [[Comilla District|Comilla]]\n| country = [[Bangladesh]]\n| location_map       = Bangladesh\n| coordinates = \n| locblock   = \n| offonshore = onshore\n| operator   = BAPEX\n| partner    = \n| image = \n| caption = \n| discovery = 2012\n| startofproduction = \n| peakofproduction =\n| expectedabandonment =\n| oil_production_bbl/d    = \n| production_gas_mmcuft/d = 41-44\n| estimatedstoiip = \n| est_gas_bft = \n| producingformations = \n}}\n'''Srikail Gas Field''' ({{lang-bn|\u09b6\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0\u0995\u09be\u0987\u09b2 \u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0}}) is a natural gas field located in [[Comilla District|Comilla]], [[Bangladesh]].<ref name=\"bbc\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/bengali/news/2012/07/120713_mb_shrikail_gas|title=\u0995\u09c1\u09ae\u09bf\u09b2\u09cd\u09b2\u09be\u09b0 \u09b6\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0\u0995\u09be\u0987\u09b2\u09c7 \u09a8\u09a4\u09c1\u09a8 \u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0\u09c7\u09b0 \u09b8\u09a8\u09cd\u09a7\u09be\u09a8|language=bn |newspaper=[[BBC Bangla]]|date=13 July 2012|access-date=31 July 2019}}</ref> It is controlled by Bangladesh Petroleum Exploration and Production Company Limited (BAPEX).<ref name=\"bapex\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bapex.com.bd/?page_id=29789 |title=Completed Project |language=bn |publisher=[[Bangladesh National Portal]]|access-date=31 July 2019}}</ref>\n==Location==\nSrikail gas field is located in Srikail village of Shrikail union, [[Muradnagar Upazila]], Comilla district, [[Chittagong Division]].<ref name=\"pa\">{{cite web|url=https://www.prothomalo.com/bangladesh/article/528961 |title=\u09a4\u09bf\u09a8 \u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0\u09c7 \u099c\u09be\u09a4\u09c0\u09af\u09bc \u09b8\u09cd\u09ac\u09be\u09b0\u09cd\u09a5 \u0989\u09aa\u09c7\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09bf\u09a4|language=bn |newspaper=[[Prothom Alo]]|date=16 May 2015|access-date=31 July 2019}}</ref> It is 7km away from the [[Bangura gas field]] and lies in the same landscape, and these two fielde are spread over an area of 140 km<sup>2</sup>.<ref name=\"bdn\">{{cite web|url=https://banglanews24.com/power-fuel/news/bd/407289.details |title=\u09ac\u09be\u0999\u09cd\u0997\u09c1\u09b0\u09be\u09b0 \u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8 \u09a8\u09bf\u09a4\u09c7 \u09aa\u09c7\u099f\u09cd\u09b0\u09cb\u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be \u0986\u0997\u09cd\u09b0\u09b9\u09c0 \u09a8\u09af\u09bc \u0995\u09c7\u09a8!|language=bn |newspaper=banglanews24.com|date=6 May 2015|access-date=31 July 2019}}</ref>\n== Production ==\nBAPEX announced the discovery of the Srikail gas field in 2004, but the service could not continue due to faulty excavation; later in 2012, the well was excavated again.<ref name=\"bbc\"/><ref name=\"dw\">{{cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/bn/\u0995\u09c1\u09ae\u09bf\u09b2\u09cd\u09b2\u09be\u09b0-\u09b6\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0\u0995\u09be\u0987\u09b2\u09c7-\u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8-\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0-\u0996\u09c1\u0981\u099c\u09c7-\u09aa\u09c7\u09b2-\u09ac\u09be\u09aa\u09c7\u0995\u09cd\u09b8/a-16095887-0 |title=\u0995\u09c1\u09ae\u09bf\u09b2\u09cd\u09b2\u09be\u09b0 \u09b6\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0\u0995\u09be\u0987\u09b2\u09c7 \u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8 \u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0 \u0996\u09c1\u0981\u099c\u09c7 \u09aa\u09c7\u09b2 \u09ac\u09be\u09aa\u09c7\u0995\u09cd\u09b8 |language=bn |newspaper=[[dw]] Bangla|date=13 July 2012|access-date=1 Aug 2019}}</ref> From May 5, to June 30, 2012, the gas was found at a depth of 3,218 meters.<ref name=\"dw\"/>\n\nIt is a medium-sized gas field.<ref name=\"bbc\"/> According to BAPEX, the total gas reserves in this field is 300 [[billion cubic feet]] (BCF).<ref name=\"dw\"/> Currently, the gas field is lifting 41-44 million cubic feet of gas per day by its two wells and providing them to the [[national grid (Bangladesh)|national grid]].<ref name=\"bdn\"/>\n== See also ==\n*[[List of natural gas fields in Bangladesh]]\n*[[Bangladesh Gas Fields Company Limited]]\n*[[Gas Transmission Company Limited]]\n==References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{Natural gas fields in Bangladesh}}\n{{Comilla District}}\n[[Category:2012 establishments in Bangladesh]]\n[[Category:Natural gas fields in Bangladesh]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Oil field\n| name = Srikail Gas Field\n| region = [[Comilla District|Comilla]]\n| country = [[Bangladesh]]\n| location_map       = Bangladesh\n| coordinates = \n| locblock   = \n| offonshore = onshore\n| operator   = BAPEX\n| partner    = \n| image = \n| caption = \n| discovery = 2012\n| startofproduction = \n| peakofproduction =\n| expectedabandonment =\n| oil_production_bbl/d    = \n| production_gas_mmcuft/d = 41-44\n| estimatedstoiip = \n| est_gas_bft = \n| producingformations = \n}}\n'''Srikail Gas Field''' ({{lang-bn|\u09b6\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0\u0995\u09be\u0987\u09b2 \u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0}}) is a natural gas field located in [[Comilla District|Comilla]], [[Bangladesh]].<ref name=\"bbc\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/bengali/news/2012/07/120713_mb_shrikail_gas|title=\u0995\u09c1\u09ae\u09bf\u09b2\u09cd\u09b2\u09be\u09b0 \u09b6\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0\u0995\u09be\u0987\u09b2\u09c7 \u09a8\u09a4\u09c1\u09a8 \u0997\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09b8\u0995\u09cd\u09b7\u09c7\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0\u09c7\u09b0 \u09b8\u09a8\u09cd\u09a7\u09be\u09a8|language=bn |newspaper=[[BBC Bangla]]|date=13 July 2012|access-date=31 July 2019}}</ref> It is controlled by Bangladesh Petroleum Exploration and Production Company Limited (BAPEX).<ref name=\"bapex\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bapex.com.bd/?page_id=29789 |title=Completed Project |language=bn |publisher=[[Bangladesh National Portal]]|access-date=31 July 2019}}</ref>\n==Location==\nSrikail gas field is located in Srikail village of Shrikail union, [[Muradnagar Upazila]], Comilla district, [[Chittagong Division]].<ref n