\"/>\n\nIt is a medium-sized gas field.<ref name=\"bbc\"/> According to BAPEX, the total gas reserves in this field is 300 [[billion cubic feet]] (BCF).<ref name=\"dw\"/> Currently, the gas field is lifting 41-44 million cubic feet of gas per day by it's two wells and providing them to the [[national grid (Bangladesh)|national grid]].<ref name=\"bdn\"/>\n== See also ==\n*[[List of natural gas fields in Bangladesh]]\n*[[Bangladesh Gas Fields Company Limited]]\n*[[Gas Transmission Company Limited]]\n==References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{Natural gas fields in Bangladesh}}\n{{Comilla District}}\n[[Category:2012 establishments in Bangladesh]]\n[[Category:Natural gas fields in Bangladesh]]\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eProduction:Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: it's \u2192 its", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Srikail_Gas_Field"}
